    "This app is provided as a supplementary aid only. Voice alerts are based on sensor data that may be inaccurate, delayed, or unavailable.\n\nThe pilot in command remains solely responsible for all decisions during flight. Never rely on this app as a primary source of information.\n\nThe developer assumes no liability for any damage, injury, or loss arising from the use of this app." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese App dient ausschließlich als ergänzendes Hilfsmittel. Sprachansagen basieren auf Sensordaten, die ungenau, verzögert oder nicht verfügbar sein können.\n\nDer verantwortliche Pilot trägt die alleinige Verantwortung für alle Entscheidungen während des Fluges. Verlassen Sie sich niemals auf diese App als primäre Informationsquelle.\n\nDer Entwickler übernimmt keine Haftung für Schäden, Verletzungen oder Verluste, die aus der Nutzung dieser App entstehen."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Questa app è fornita esclusivamente come ausilio supplementare. Gli avvisi vocali si basano su dati dei sensori che possono essere imprecisi, in ritardo o non disponibili.\n\nIl pilota in comando resta l'unico responsabile di tutte le decisioni durante il volo. Non fare mai affidamento su questa app come fonte primaria di informazioni.\n\nLo sviluppatore non si assume alcuna responsabilità per danni, lesioni o perdite derivanti dall'uso di questa app."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This app is provided as a supplementary aid only. Voice alerts are based on sensor data that may be inaccurate, delayed, or unavailable. The pilot in command remains solely responsible for all decisions during flight. Never rely on this app as a primary source of information. The developer assumes no liability for any damage, injury, or loss arising from the use of this app." : {
